==German==
===Etymology===
From the notion that turkish people would smell like  [[caraway]], or probably rather the quite distinct ''[[Kreuzkümmel]]'' "cumin".
===Noun===
'''Kümmeltürke''' ''f''
# very derogative and xenophobic term for a [[turkish]] person, or rather anyone coming from a culture that has food rich in spices
